        "text": "Nehemiah 10:36",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ".). The suffix to וטהרתּים refers to the Jews. נכר, strange, means foreign heathen customs, and chiefly marriages with heathen women, ",
